[normal]we have
[normal] 
[normal]seen 
[normal]a substantial and sustained 
[normal]i
[normal]ncrease
[normal] in application
[normal]s
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]Between 199
[normal]7 and 2011
[normal] t
[normal]he Commission 
[normal]typically 
[normal]receive
[normal]d
[normal] 
[normal]around 900 
[normal]applications
[normal] per year
[normal]. In 
[normal]the business year 2011/12 we received 1,040 applications
[normal]; 
[normal]in
[normal] 2012/13
[normal] that rose to 1
[normal],
[normal]625.
[normal] 
[normal]We expect 
[normal]case intake to remain at 
[normal]around 
