[normal] it 
[normal]currently
[normal] takes an average of 19 weeks to reach an
[normal] initial decision. For 
[normal]those
[normal] other
[normal] case
[normal]s
[normal] that
[normal] 
[normal]do 
[normal]go on to receive a full review, it takes a
[normal]n average
[normal] of
[normal] 21 weeks
[normal] to reach initial decision stage
[normal]. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]22
[normal]              
[normal]See 
[normal]annex A
[normal] for 
[normal]average waiting times
[normal] 
