[normal]to 
[normal]fulfil our functions, to reach potential a
[normal]pplicants and
[normal] raise informed awareness of our role
[normal],
[normal] and
[normal] 
[normal]help us feed
[normal] 
[normal]back our findings 
[normal]to the criminal justice system at large.
